### Welcome to My project ### Hi there,

This is my first git hub project ever started and truly excited !

Well, I wanted to start by coding basic data structures in C. So i have uploaded single and double linked list programs. Please download them and refer to README to see how to compile and run. [Click for Documentation](https://github.com/janipallisuresh/DataStructures/blob/MyDS/Doc/index.html) ### Authors and Contributors Suresh Janipalli (@janipallisuresh).
